      "title": "GIANTS Software | Home",
      "description": "GIANTS Software company page",
      "text_excerpt": "GIANTS Software | Home\nDiscover GIANTS Software!\nWe are the creators behind the globally renowned Farming Simulator series. But our expertise extends beyond development—we’re also a publisher, engine developers, modding enthusiasts, and more. Plus, we’re growing our team!\nJoin the GIANTS Software team!\nWhether you're a talented programmer, a dynamic marketing professional, a creative graphic designer or video editor, a dedicated community manager, or a skilled event organizer, we're always looking to expand our team. Visit our careers page to learn more!\nGet in Touch with GIANTS Software!\nWe are always looking to meet new people, make new contacts, start new partnerships. Whether for the game, if you are interested in representation of your brand, or for a professional or casual exchange at events. Feel free to contact us, anytime!\nLATEST NEWS\nGIANTS Software will be part of the PAX East line-up again.\nWe will once again be at one of the world’s most celebrated gaming culture events, presenting the successful Farming Simulator franchise and the latest version of Project Motor Racing.\nFrom March 26th to the 29th, we are looking forward to meeting fans and friends at the Thomas M. Menino Convention & Exhibition Center in Boston (MA).\nWith a wide variety of interesting panels and gaming exhibits, as well as stage shows, PAX East visitors can expect to have hours of fun meeting old friends and making new ones. Find out more about PAX East on the official event website.\nMore\nFarming Simulator: Signature Edition is out now on Nintendo Switch™ 2. From managing fields and forests to raising livestock and building a thriving agricultural empire, Farming Simulator: Signature Edition offers endless possibilities: Production chains, construction projects, and a broad range of farming activities await both seasoned players and newfound farmers.\n“Farming Simulator: Signature Edition offers the most varied, relaxing, and rewarding experience we’ve ever created for Nintendo players,” says Boris Stefan, CSO of GIANTS Software. “We’re excited to bring the farming fun to the Nintendo Switch 2!”\nThe Signature Farming Experience\nPlayers can choose from three vibrant regions as their starting point and grow their skills across a variety of agricultural scenarios: North America, Europe, and East Asia. With 25 crops, including rice, spinach, wheat, and sunflowers, plus greenhouse produce and various tree species, the farming experience is richer than ever.\nWith over 400 meticulously recreated machines from more than 150 well-known manufacturers, including Case IH, CLAAS, Fendt, John Deere, Kubota, Massey Ferguson, New Holland, Valtra, and many more, Farming Simulator: Signature Edition delivers authenticity for both machinery fans and simulation enthusiasts.\nMore Content Planned\nThe recent deal between GIANTS Software and Daimler Truck AG, which saw the debut of Mercedes-Benz Trucks in the series, is also incorporated into the Signature Edition.  As always, GIANTS Softw"
    },
